   <|"Data" -> "speaker.md\n## Introduction\nHello everyone. I am Kirill \
Vasin from the University of Augsburg,\nand I would love to share with you an \
altermagnet candidate Fe2Mo3O8 that shows an unusually large Faraday \
rotation.", "Display" -> "codemirror", 
    "Hash" -> "31ca296c-28b1-41b3-bf4b-d2fa8cbcf0e1", "Invisible" -> False, 
    "MetaOnly" -> False, "Props" -> <||>, "PublicFields" -> {"Properties"}, 
