   <|"Data" -> "Slide itself:", "Display" -> "markdown", 
    "Hash" -> "3178fca4-7eff-4684-8e73-ad71eb8335ab", "Invisible" -> False, 
    "MetaOnly" -> False, "Props" -> <||>, "PublicFields" -> {"Properties"}, 
    "State" -> "Idle", "Type" -> "Output", "UID" -> Null, 
    "Notebook" -> "9d01a796-6ef9-4d6d-bafa-4fb630c0bb77"|>, 
   <|"Data" -> ".slide\n\n<!-- .slide: class=\"slide-standard slide-dark\" \
data-background-color=\"black\" -->\n\n<MakeTitle>Fe<sub>2</sub> \
Mo<sub>3</sub> O<sub>8</sub> is</MakeTitle>\n\n<Columns>\n <div \
style=\"z-index: -1;position: \
relative\"><InteractiveCrystalStructure/></div>\n <div \
style=\"font-size:smaller; text-align:left\">\n\n  <br/>\n\n\n  - collinear \
antiferromagnet $\\text{T}_\\text{N} = 60~\\text{K}$\n  - hexagonal polar \
dielectric $6_{3}mm$ \n  - magnetoelectric\n  - an altermagnet candidate (no \
$\\text{PT}$ element)\n\n  <br/>\n\n  #### Magnetically active ions \n\n  \
<div>\n\n  </div>\n  \n  - A-site $\\text{Fe}^{2+} \\text{(S=2, L=2)}$ \
__tetrahedron__\n  - B-site $\\text{Fe}^{2+} \\text{(S=2, L=2)}$ \
__octahedron__\n\n\n  <figure class=\"flex flex-row items-center\">\n     \n  \
\n  <img src=\"/attachments/tokuraj-6bc.png\" class=\"dark-content\" \
width=\"270\"/>\n\n     \n  <caption><span class=\"text-xs\">QIAN CHEN et al. \
Phys. Rev. B 109 2024</span></caption>\n  </figure>\n \n</div> \n\n \n\n \
\n</Columns>\n\n<Footer/>", "Display" -> "codemirror", 
